3675	  functor \(\mathrm{Opens.map}\,\varphi_{\mathrm{inv}}^{\mathrm{base}}\) is \(\mathrm{Final}\), which
3676	  holds by \cref{lem:opens_map_final_of_scheme_iso} (itself from the equivalence
3677	  \cref{def:opens_map_equiv_of_iso}). Its inverse is the asserted unit isomorphism.
3678	\end{proof}
