  % `haveI`. (2) After that, a coercion mismatch `↥V` vs `↥↑V`: `unitToPushforwardObjUnit` infers its
  % `K` topology from `R := V.toScheme.ringCatSheaf` (space printed `↥↑V`), which does not unify with
